Gros Warns Against D-Mark Return to Solve Crisis, Welt Reports

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-08-13T11:11:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/gros-warns-against-d-mark-return-to-solve-crisis-welt-reports.html
Daniel Gros , director of the Centre
for European Policy Studies in Brussels, said a return to the
deutsche mark would caused  Germany ’s financial and banking
system to “collapse completely,”  Welt am Sonntag  reported.  Banks wouldn’t lend money to each other anymore and the
German economy would “nosedive,” the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
